This is the instruction of how to use the Makefile and how to play the game:

How to use Make file
make play --->  start to play game


How to play the game:
1. At the beginning of the game, enter the game board size you want. 
   Please just enter numbers, no space or other characters.

2. Please type "L" for moving left
   Please type "R" for moving right
   Please type "U" for moving up
   Please type "D" for moving down
   Please type "Q" for ending the game

3. If a game ends, either because no more moves can be made or the user exits the game, please type "make expt" in the 
   terminal to if you want to start a new game. 
